      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 2,
        "width": 346,
        "height": 538,
        "content": "## Form intake mapping\n\nStarts the workflow from a submitted form and converts the selected industry or search criteria into values suitable for the scraping step.\n\n**TIP:** `locationQuery` takes ONE location per run — use `City, Country` (e.g. \"Austin, USA\"); a whole country is too broad and fills the cap fast. The Industry list is a baked-in snapshot of HubSpot's official industries."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "5a78b104-2bb5-456c-89ae-f883fa4c070d",
      "name": "About and Setup",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -2448,
        -288
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 620,
        "height": 754,
        "content": "## 🗺️ Google Maps Lead Generation for HubSpot CRM\n\n### ⚙️ How it works\n\nThis workflow collects lead-generation criteria from a form, maps the selected industry, and runs an Apify Google Maps actor to scrape businesses. It extracts and deduplicates company data, checks HubSpot for existing companies, then updates or creates company records. For companies with domains, it uses Hunter to find contacts, deduplicates them, and upserts the contacts into HubSpot.\n\n### 🧩 Setup steps\n\n- [ ] Configure the form trigger fields used for location, industry, search terms, and any other Apify actor inputs.\n- [ ] Connect Apify credentials and set the Google Maps actor plus dataset retrieval settings to match the actor output.\n- [ ] Connect HubSpot credentials with permissions to search, create, and update companies and contacts.\n- [ ] Connect Hunter credentials for domain search, and confirm the workflow passes a valid company domain or website to Hunter.\n- [ ] Review mapped HubSpot properties such as company name, domain, website, rating, category, average price, and contact fields.\n\n### 🛠️ Customization\n\nAdjust the Map Industry code, Apify actor inputs, duplicate-matching keys, HubSpot property mappings, and Hunter contact filtering rules to target different markets or qualification criteria."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "d680d50a-6748-4ba9-a1dc-737d7514bf30",
