        "content": "## Match HubSpot companies\n\nSearches HubSpot for existing companies, normalizes the search result, and merges it back with the deduplicated scraped company data."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "846e38df-9f81-48b6-a93d-4d8788f9ddb5",
      "name": "Sticky Note6",
