      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 2,
        "width": 640,
        "height": 640,
        "content": "## Upsert company records\n\nDetermines whether each company already exists in HubSpot, updates existing records or creates new ones, then standardizes the resulting company details for contact enrichment."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "0ffc7b59-93f4-4d66-b64a-7f725bd2b731",
      "name": "Sticky Note7",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1008,
        -192
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 2,
        "width": 416,
        "height": 480,
        "content": "## Find domain contacts\n\nFilters companies to those with a domain and uses Hunter domain search to discover associated contacts.\n\n**Hunter free tier:** 25 searches + 50 verifications / month. Domain Search costs 1 credit per email, so `limit` is kept low (10) and filtered to personal emails."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
